nowledge them as valid tools for making an emulator more accurate.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Portability perhaps?</div><br />Not by itself, I think. If it doesn't offer anything else, will there be any interest in porting it?<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">- That's why I'm avoiding personal opinions about my emulator; it's not the case.</div>
